Comment: 0,0:01:48.96,0:01:51.00,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,Correct. Well done.
Comment: 0,0:01:51.00,0:01:53.21,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,Thank you. Please have a seat.
Comment: 0,0:01:53.21,0:01:56.67,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,So, it's best not to rely on anyone, ever.
Comment: 0,0:02:29.33,0:02:32.42,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,It's true that I don't know a thing about working,
