Comment: 0,0:02:35.76,0:02:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,If you can't accept that, you shouldn't be here.
Comment: 0,0:02:37.72,0:02:39.47,Default,Minchi,0,0,0,,Do you understand the concept of "work"?
Comment: 0,0:02:41.47,0:02:42.76,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,I'll show them.
Comment: 0,0:02:43.30,0:02:46.77,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Something my mother, that\N useless woman, taught me is...
Comment: 0,0:02:47.81,0:02:51.56,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,You promised! Why didn't you come?
Comment: 0,0:02:53.31,0:02:54.36,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,Ohana!
Comment: 0,0:02:54.71,0:02:57.44,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,Mark my words: people can't be trusted.
Comment: 0,0:02:57.44,0:02:59.32,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,Not even family.
Comment: 0,0:02:59.65,0:03:01.28,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,Never rely on someone else.
Comment: 0,0:03:01.28,0:03:02.87,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,Believe only in yourself.
Comment: 0,0:03:03.41,0:03:05.12,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,That's not even what—
Comment: 0,0:03:05.12,0:03:09.00,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,What you need to do, is get them before they get you.
Comment: 0,0:03:09.00,0:03:11.46,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,Gouge them. Cut them down.
Comment: 0,0:03:11.46,0:03:12.88,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Cut them down?
Comment: 0,0:03:12.88,0:03:15.34,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,Yes. Cut.
Comment: 0,0:03:15.63,0:03:16.88,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Cut them down!
Comment: 0,0:03:18.17,0:03:19.09,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Cut them down!
