Comment: 0,0:03:24.18,0:03:25.97,Default,Tomoe,0,0,0,,Huh? Good morning!
Comment: 0,0:03:26.33,0:03:29.27,Default,Tomoe,0,0,0,,Hard at work at five in the morning?
