Comment: 0,0:03:32.27,0:03:33.19,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Nah...
Comment: 0,0:03:33.19,0:03:35.27,Default,Grand,0,0,0,,She's not accomplishing nearly as much as she thinks.
Comment: 0,0:03:36.40,0:03:38.61,Default,Grand,0,0,0,,You're not cutting them short enough.
Comment: 0,0:03:38.61,0:03:40.49,Default,,0,0,0,,They'll just grow right back.
Comment: 0,0:03:40.49,0:03:42.70,Default,Grand,0,0,0,,Careless effort does nothing but harm.
Comment: 0,0:03:45.12,0:03:46.66,Default,Tomoe,0,0,0,,Harsh.
Comment: 0,0:03:47.08,0:03:49.58,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,I'm not too fond of Grandma.
Comment: 0,0:03:50.04,0:03:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, "Madam Manager".
Comment: 0,0:03:52.62,0:03:54.04,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,But that's why I'll...
Comment: 0,0:03:55.21,0:03:56.88,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Cut them down!
Comment: 0,0:04:00.05,0:04:01.30,Default,Grand,0,0,0,,Come with me.
Comment: 0,0:04:04.90,0:04:07.30,Default,Nako,0,0,0,,M-Me?
Comment: 0,0:04:07.70,0:04:10.93,Default,Grand,0,0,0,,A new waitress should learn from one more experienced.
