Comment: 0,0:04:20.48,0:04:23.70,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Although, I'm not old enough to drink alcohol.
Comment: 0,0:04:24.70,0:04:26.91,Default,Grand,0,0,0,,You will not be required to attend banquets.
Comment: 0,0:04:26.91,0:04:28.78,Default,Grand,0,0,0,,However, all other duties must be performed perfectly.
Comment: 0,0:04:29.20,0:04:31.95,Default,Grand,0,0,0,,As of today, Ohana will be under your wing.
Comment: 0,0:04:32.58,0:04:33.66,Default,Grand,0,0,0,,Have I made myself clear?
