Comment: 0,0:04:36.38,0:04:37.08,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Huh?
Comment: 0,0:04:52.52,0:04:55.10,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,I wish I could wear it like you.
Comment: 0,0:04:56.10,0:04:57.90,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,You look dazzling!
Comment: 0,0:04:57.90,0:05:00.07,Default,Nako,0,0,0,,C-Come on...
Comment: 0,0:05:00.07,0:05:02.03,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Not a single wasted motion.
Comment: 0,0:05:02.03,0:05:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Your gestures are so elegant!
Comment: 0,0:05:03.78,0:05:08.37,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Plus, you're tall, so I bet you're great at sports!
Comment: 0,0:05:08.37,0:05:09.28,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,You've gotta be!
Comment: 0,0:05:09.28,0:05:09.76,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Huh?
Comment: 0,0:05:12.91,0:05:15.37,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Even I should be able to do a decent job at cleaning.
