Comment: 0,0:05:20.17,0:05:21.42,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Why not?
Comment: 0,0:05:21.42,0:05:22.96,Default,Nako,0,0,0,,B-Because.
Comment: 0,0:05:24.34,0:05:26.72,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Okay then, I won't step on it!
