Comment: 0,0:06:00.67,0:06:02.21,Default,Nako,0,0,0,,C-Coming!
Comment: 0,0:06:04.05,0:06:06.42,Default,Nako,0,0,0,,I-I'll be right back.
Comment: 0,0:06:07.55,0:06:09.76,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,O...kay...?
Comment: 0,0:06:14.64,0:06:18.10,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,"Never rely on someone else. Believe only in yourself."
Comment: 0,0:06:18.89,0:06:20.56,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,That's what my mother taught me.
Comment: 0,0:06:21.81,0:06:26.99,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,I suppose I should go ahead and clean this room.
