Comment: 0,0:06:39.71,0:06:41.83,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,So this must be...
Comment: 0,0:06:41.83,0:06:44.04,Default,Tomoe,0,0,0,,He stays in the Wave Room.
Comment: 0,0:06:44.59,0:06:47.09,Default,Tomoe,0,0,0,,Rumor has it he's a famous author.
Comment: 0,0:06:48.13,0:06:50.80,Default,Tomoe,0,0,0,,I'm not much of a reader, so I don't know his name,
Comment: 0,0:06:50.80,0:06:52.68,Default,Tomoe,0,0,0,,but I hear he's something else!
