Comment: 0,0:07:40.89,0:07:43.19,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Don't lose heart, Ohana!
Comment: 0,0:07:46.07,0:07:49.23,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Relying on others will only cause you pain.
