Comment: 0,0:08:12.72,0:08:13.55,Default,Tohru,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Comment: 0,0:08:13.55,0:08:14.89,Default,Minchi,0,0,0,,Umm, and the staff's breakfast?
Comment: 0,0:08:14.89,0:08:15.97,Default,Tohru,0,0,0,,Not this morning!
Comment: 0,0:08:15.97,0:08:17.89,Default,Tohru,0,0,0,,There's no time to cook for them.
Comment: 0,0:08:17.89,0:08:18.89,Default,Tohru,0,0,0,,Get to work!
Comment: 0,0:08:18.89,0:08:19.81,Default,Minchi,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
