Comment: 0,0:10:18.22,0:10:21.85,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,...a phrase that was somehow familiar.{I don't think she's actually referencing anything.}
Comment: 0,0:10:23.85,0:10:27.27,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,The draft I've been working on\N non-stop since coming here has vanished!
Comment: 0,0:10:27.27,0:10:28.23,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,You hear me?
Comment: 0,0:10:28.23,0:10:29.56,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,It's the work of the century!
Comment: 0,0:10:29.56,0:10:31.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It might very well win the Naoki Prize!
Comment: 0,0:10:31.81,0:10:33.32,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,Do you understand?!
Comment: 0,0:10:33.32,0:10:34.15,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,What's all this about?
Comment: 0,0:10:34.98,0:10:37.24,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,That's the girl who cleaned my room, isn't it?
Comment: 0,0:10:37.24,0:10:37.82,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,You!
Comment: 0,0:10:38.82,0:10:41.53,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,You! You! You! You!
Comment: 0,0:10:41.53,0:10:42.70,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,New girl!
Comment: 0,0:10:42.70,0:10:44.62,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,Was this your doing?!
Comment: 0,0:10:45.66,0:10:46.45,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Huh?
Comment: 0,0:10:50.79,0:10:54.92,Default,Grand,0,0,0,,You're absolutely positive that all you did was clean?
Comment: 0,0:10:54.92,0:10:56.17,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Y-Yes.
Comment: 0,0:10:56.55,0:10:59.17,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,I did throw out the papers that were in the trash, but that's all.
Comment: 0,0:10:59.17,0:11:00.63,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,Unbelievable.
Comment: 0,0:11:01.39,0:11:02.93,Default,Grand,0,0,0,,Shall we call the police?
Comment: 0,0:11:02.93,0:11:04.97,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,No, that's all right.
Comment: 0,0:11:04.97,0:11:05.81,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,There's no need for that.
Comment: 0,0:11:05.81,0:11:06.81,Default,Grand,0,0,0,,But...
Comment: 0,0:11:06.81,0:11:10.69,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,I want to compete with the quality of my work.
Comment: 0,0:11:11.06,0:11:13.61,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,If it's made famous simply because of this scandal,
Comment: 0,0:11:13.61,0:11:16.07,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,it won't receive a fair evaluation.
Comment: 0,0:11:16.48,0:11:17.94,Default,Grand,0,0,0,,I understand.
Comment: 0,0:11:17.94,0:11:22.07,Default,Grand,0,0,0,,My entire staff will search for the draft in question.
Comment: 0,0:11:22.07,0:11:25.62,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,I'll be holding you responsible if it's not found.
Comment: 0,0:11:26.79,0:11:28.45,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,Meaning, my stay here will be free of charge.
Comment: 0,0:11:29.79,0:11:32.12,Default,Grand,0,0,0,,Yes, of course.
Comment: 0,0:11:42.68,0:11:45.39,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,Mother, that jerk's been here at least a month—
Comment: 0,0:11:45.39,0:11:46.18,Default,Grand,0,0,0,,Madam Manager.
Comment: 0,0:11:47.18,0:11:49.10,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,What shall we do, Madam Manager?
Comment: 0,0:11:49.60,0:11:53.27,Default,Grand,0,0,0,,We are not to clean the Wave Room without the customer's supervision.
Comment: 0,0:11:55.90,0:11:57.86,Default,Grand,0,0,0,,Did Nako not tell you this?
Comment: 0,0:11:58.61,0:12:01.03,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,She did, I'm sorry.
Comment: 0,0:12:01.65,0:12:05.12,Default,Grand,0,0,0,,It's commendable that you're taking initiative.
Comment: 0,0:12:05.49,0:12:06.53,Default,Grand,0,0,0,,But I warned you.
Comment: 0,0:12:08.29,0:12:10.54,Default,Grand,0,0,0,,Careless effort does nothing but harm.
Comment: 0,0:12:11.66,0:12:13.75,Default,Tomoe,0,0,0,,Ma'am, that's—
Comment: 0,0:12:14.50,0:12:16.79,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,What do you want from me?
Comment: 0,0:12:17.25,0:12:19.88,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,You told me I don't understand what it means to work,
Comment: 0,0:12:19.88,0:12:22.01,Default,,0,0,0,,so I was trying my hardest to learn.
Comment: 0,0:12:22.01,0:12:24.13,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,I'm doing my best...
Comment: 0,0:12:24.64,0:12:25.89,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,But after all that...
Comment: 0,0:12:27.43,0:12:29.81,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,I'm going to look for the draft.
Comment: 0,0:12:29.81,0:12:31.14,Default,Grand,0,0,0,,No, don't.
Comment: 0,0:12:33.56,0:12:36.56,Default,Grand,0,0,0,,I can't have you making another mistake.
Comment: 0,0:12:37.19,0:12:39.57,Default,Grand,0,0,0,,Return to your regular duties.
Comment: 0,0:12:41.61,0:12:43.78,Default,Tomoe,0,0,0,,She's acting so strangely today.
Comment: 0,0:12:44.11,0:12:48.83,Default,Tomoe,0,0,0,,She'd usually stop at nothing\N to fulfill a customer's request.
Comment: 0,0:12:54.46,0:13:00.63,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,I've thought about rebelling,\N but I don't even know how to.
Comment: 0,0:13:01.09,0:13:05.18,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Maybe I should be like Mom, and start flirting with boys.
Comment: 0,0:13:10.56,0:13:12.10,Default,Tohru,0,0,0,,Hey, kid.
Comment: 0,0:13:12.47,0:13:14.69,Default,Tohru,0,0,0,,If you've got nothing to do, come with me.
Comment: 0,0:13:15.02,0:13:18.19,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,"Kid"? Are you talking to me?
Comment: 0,0:13:18.19,0:13:19.94,Default,Tohru,0,0,0,,I don't see anyone else here.
Comment: 0,0:13:19.94,0:13:24.53,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Don't you think it's rude to address someone that way?
Comment: 0,0:13:24.53,0:13:26.03,Default,Tohru,0,0,0,,Just hop in.
Comment: 0,0:13:32.08,0:13:34.75,Default,Tohru,0,0,0,,There's going to be a ton of stuff to carry.
Comment: 0,0:13:34.75,0:13:37.00,Default,Tohru,0,0,0,,But you've got big biceps,
Comment: 0,0:13:37.00,0:13:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,and you look pretty strong,\N so you'll be perfect for the job.
Comment: 0,0:13:39.88,0:13:44.17,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,I-I highly doubt you can see\N my biceps through these sleeves.
Comment: 0,0:13:42.17,0:13:49.76,Default,Tohru,0,0,0,,{\an8}Once you're prepared to deal with the pain of loss...
Comment: 0,0:13:47.80,0:13:49.76,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,I'm not too fond of this guy.
Comment: 0,0:13:50.68,0:13:51.81,Default,Tohru,0,0,0,,Say...
Comment: 0,0:13:51.81,0:13:52.64,Default,Ohara,0,0,0,,Yes?
Comment: 0,0:13:52.64,0:13:54.10,Default,Tohru,0,0,0,,You don't have any friends, do you?
Comment: 0,0:13:54.52,0:13:55.64,Default,Ohara,0,0,0,,What?!
Comment: 0,0:13:55.64,0:13:58.90,Default,Ohara,0,0,0,,How rude! I do so!
Comment: 0,0:14:03.68,0:14:06.24,Default,Ko,0,0,0,,I've always liked you, Matsumae Ohana!
Comment: 0,0:14:09.49,0:14:11.28,Default,Tohru,0,0,0,,Yeah, sure. Doesn't look that way.
Comment: 0,0:14:11.28,0:14:14.20,Default,Tohru,0,0,0,,You don't seem very considerate, is all.
Comment: 0,0:14:14.20,0:14:16.50,Default,Ohara,0,0,0,,Right back at you.
Comment: 0,0:14:16.50,0:14:19.00,Default,Tohru,0,0,0,,Well, you're pretty uncooperative.
Comment: 0,0:14:19.00,0:14:21.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like you're blind to what's going on around you.
Comment: 0,0:14:21.46,0:14:24.25,Default,Ohara,0,0,0,,I decided a long time ago not to rely on other people.
Comment: 0,0:14:25.80,0:14:28.18,Default,Tohru,0,0,0,,Oh, but can you rely on yourself?
Comment: 0,0:14:29.47,0:14:34.22,Default,Tohru,0,0,0,,Are you so amazing you can do everything by yourself?
Comment: 0,0:14:36.77,0:14:39.94,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Let me rephrase that. I seriously dislike this guy.
Comment: 0,0:14:40.52,0:14:45.44,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,What's the best word to hurt\N someone in situations like these?
Comment: 0,0:14:49.24,0:14:49.99,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Die.
Comment: 0,0:14:51.37,0:14:52.16,Default,Tohru,0,0,0,,Huh?
Comment: 0,0:14:53.91,0:14:56.14,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,J-Just kidding! You didn't hear that!
Comment: 0,0:14:56.14,0:14:57.29,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,I was joking!
Comment: 0,0:15:05.30,0:15:06.84,Default,Tohru,0,0,0,,What the heck is your problem?!
Comment: 0,0:15:06.84,0:15:08.01,Default,Tohru,0,0,0,,You trying to kill me?!
Comment: 0,0:15:08.01,0:15:09.67,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Dying is bad.
Comment: 0,0:15:10.94,0:15:13.64,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Don't die! That'd be awful!
Comment: 0,0:15:13.64,0:15:15.10,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,I have to go.
Comment: 0,0:15:19.56,0:15:23.02,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Please drive carefully, Tooru.
Comment: 0,0:15:23.90,0:15:25.40,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Come home safe!
Comment: 0,0:15:26.65,0:15:28.07,Default,Tohru,0,0,0,,H-Hey!
Comment: 0,0:15:28.90,0:15:30.99,Default,Tohru,0,0,0,,What am I gonna do about the luggage?!
Comment: 0,0:15:30.99,0:15:32.82,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,You'll figure something out!
Comment: 0,0:15:44.84,0:15:47.30,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,What's wrong with me?
Comment: 0,0:15:47.67,0:15:49.80,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Why do I feel so mixed-up inside?
Comment: 0,0:15:50.17,0:15:52.93,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,I thought I just wanted to work.
Comment: 0,0:15:55.12,0:15:57.47,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,But is that really all?
Comment: 0,0:15:58.47,0:16:02.60,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,I didn't actually come here to work...
Comment: 0,0:16:02.60,0:16:05.56,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,But now... I want to prove myself to them.
Comment: 0,0:16:07.94,0:16:11.32,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,What is it that I really want to do?
Comment: 0,0:16:14.82,0:16:17.41,Default,Tohru,0,0,0,,Oh, but can you rely on yourself?
Comment: 0,0:16:18.08,0:16:19.16,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Rely...
Comment: 0,0:16:20.29,0:16:23.79,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,On that day, I decided to stop relying on others.
Comment: 0,0:16:24.25,0:16:27.79,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,So why am I so confused?
Comment: 0,0:16:29.19,0:16:30.76,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Dinner's ready.
Comment: 0,0:16:32.76,0:16:34.89,Default,Satsu,0,0,0,,Thanks, Ohana!
Comment: 0,0:16:35.64,0:16:40.10,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Since broccoli was my mom's least favorite\N food, I made a ton of it for dinner that night.
Comment: 0,0:17:00.33,0:17:05.25,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Somehow, it made me feel a bit better.
Comment: 0,0:17:07.71,0:17:08.75,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Comment: 0,0:17:11.38,0:17:13.88,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,I expect to see crab on the menu tonight.
Comment: 0,0:17:14.80,0:17:18.26,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,Do you realize how much trouble you've all caused me?!
Comment: 0,0:17:18.26,0:17:19.25,Default,Minchi,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Comment: 0,0:17:19.25,0:17:20.60,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,Sheesh...
Comment: 0,0:17:21.99,0:17:22.72,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Huh?
Comment: 0,0:17:23.08,0:17:24.85,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,U-Um...
Comment: 0,0:17:30.23,0:17:32.61,Default,Minko,0,0,0,,This is your fault.
Comment: 0,0:17:33.11,0:17:34.24,Default,Minko,0,0,0,,Die.
Comment: 0,0:17:43.08,0:17:44.79,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Stop telling me to die!
Comment: 0,0:17:44.79,0:17:45.58,Default,Minko,0,0,0,,Huh?
Comment: 0,0:17:47.71,0:17:51.13,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,What if I actually did end up dying?
Comment: 0,0:17:51.13,0:17:53.09,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,You would feel bad afterwards, right?
Comment: 0,0:17:53.09,0:17:55.84,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Choose your words a bit more wisely!
Comment: 0,0:17:56.59,0:17:57.80,Default,Minko,0,0,0,,What are you...
Comment: 0,0:18:00.47,0:18:02.47,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,And you!
Comment: 0,0:18:04.27,0:18:06.35,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Stop running away all the time!
Comment: 0,0:18:06.35,0:18:08.35,Default,Minko,0,0,0,,What is with you?
Comment: 0,0:18:08.35,0:18:09.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you bossing us around?
Comment: 0,0:18:09.85,0:18:11.40,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,I'll change, too!
Comment: 0,0:18:11.98,0:18:13.40,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,I'll learn to be more considerate!
Comment: 0,0:18:13.40,0:18:15.36,Default,Minko,0,0,0,,You sure don't seem very considerate right now.
Comment: 0,0:18:15.99,0:18:18.07,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,I'll also learn to count on others!
Comment: 0,0:18:18.07,0:18:19.16,Default,Nako,0,0,0,,Beg your pardon?
Comment: 0,0:18:19.16,0:18:21.28,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,I'll count on you! I'll rely on you!
Comment: 0,0:18:21.28,0:18:25.95,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,So teach me more about work, and the things I shouldn't do!
Comment: 0,0:18:27.52,0:18:28.87,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,But not just that!
Comment: 0,0:18:29.42,0:18:31.21,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,I want to know more about you two!
